oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:title: Copy print of John William Cato, in uniform
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:description: This black and white studio portrait photograph shows John William Cato in uniform. He wears a campaign hat, long sleeved wool shirt with necktie, and breeches with canvas leggings. He is seated, with left leg crossed over right knee.
